msgstr "Kurtosis"

msgid "Std. Error of Kurtosis"
msgstr "Std. Error Kurtosis"

msgid "Shapiro-Wilk"
msgstr "Shapiro-Wilk"

msgid "P-value of Shapiro-Wilk"
msgstr "Nilai P Shapiro-Wilk"

msgid "25th percentile"
msgstr "Persentil ke-25"

msgid "50th percentile"
msgstr "Persentil ke-50"

msgid "75th percentile"
msgstr "Persentil ke-75"

msgid "%gth percentile"
msgstr "Persentil ke-%g"

msgid "Error in Percentiles, all values should >=0 and <=100"
msgstr "Kesalahan pada Persentil, semua nilai harus >=0 dan <=100"

msgid "Sum"
msgstr "Jumlah"

msgid "All values are identical"
msgstr "Semua nilai identik"

msgid ""
"Infimum (minimum) of an empty set is %1$s, supremum (maximum) of an empty "
"set is %2$s."
msgstr ""
"Infimum (minimum) dari himpunan kosong adalah %1$s, supremum (maksimum) dari "
"himpunan kosong adalah %2$s."

msgid ""
"More than one mode exists. For nominal and ordinal data, the first mode is "
"reported. For continuous data, the mode with the highest density estimate is "
"reported but multiple modes may exist. We recommend visualizing the data to "
"check for multimodality."
msgstr ""
"Terdapat lebih dari satu modus. Untuk data nominal dan ordinal, modus "
"pertama yang dilaporkan. Untuk data kontinu, modus dengan estimasi densitas "
"tertinggi yang dilaporkan, namun beberapa modus mungkin ada. Kami "
"menyarankan untuk memvisualisasikan data guna memeriksa multimodalitas."

msgid ""
"Geometric and harmonic means are defined only for strictly positive "
"variables, but the data contain some non-positive values."
msgstr ""
"Rata-rata geometrik dan harmonik hanya didefinisikan untuk variabel yang "
"bernilai positif secara ketat, namun data memuat beberapa nilai tidak "
"positif."

msgid ""
"For ordinal variables, quantile type 3 was used because the selected type is "
"not supported."
msgstr ""
"Untuk variabel ordinal, tipe kuantil 3 digunakan karena tipe yang dipilih "
"tidak didukung."

msgid "Total"
msgstr "Total"

msgid "All variables have more than %1$s distinct values"
msgstr "Semua variabel memiliki lebih dari %1$s nilai berbeda"

msgid "Frequencies"
msgstr "Frekuensi"

msgid "Frequencies for %s"
msgstr "Frekuensi untuk %s"

msgid "Frequency"
msgstr "Frekuensi"

msgid "Percent"
msgstr "Persen"

msgid "Valid Percent"
msgstr "Persen Valid"

msgid "Cumulative Percent"
msgstr "Persen Kumulatif"

msgid "Plotting not possible: %s"
msgstr "Pembuatan plot tidak memungkinkan: %s"

msgid "Plotting is not possible: No plot type selected!"
msgstr "Pembuatan plot tidak memungkinkan: Tidak ada tipe plot yang dipilih!"

msgid "Counts"
msgstr "Cacah"

msgid "Density"
msgstr "Densitas"

msgid "No non-missing values!"
msgstr "Tidak ada nilai yang tidak hilang!"

msgid ""
"Association cannot be computed due to missing values. Try a different 'Use' "
"setting."
msgstr ""
"Asosiasi tidak dapat dihitung karena nilai yang hilang. Coba pengaturan "
"'Gunakan' yang berbeda."

msgid ""
"Some associations cannot be computed due to missing values. Try a different "
"'Use' setting."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa asosiasi tidak dapat dihitung karena nilai yang hilang. Coba "
"pengaturan 'Gunakan' yang berbeda."

msgid ""
"Plotting not possible: Variable '%s' has fewer than 2 valid (non-missing) "
"observations."
msgstr ""
"Pembuatan plot tidak memungkinkan: Variabel '%s' memiliki kurang dari 2 "
"pengamatan valid (tidak hilang)."

msgid "Stem"
msgstr "Batang"

msgid "Leaf"
msgstr "Daun"

msgid ""
"A stem and leaf table could not be made because there are fewer than 2 non-"
"missing observations"
msgstr ""
"Tabel batang dan daun tidak dapat dibuat karena terdapat kurang dari 2 "
"pengamatan yang tidak hilang"

msgid "The decimal point is at the |"
msgstr "Titik desimal berada pada |"

msgid ""
"There must be a unique value per combination of levels of horizontal and "
"vertical axis!"
msgstr ""
"Harus terdapat nilai unik untuk setiap kombinasi tingkat sumbu horizontal "
"dan vertikal!"

msgid "All categorical variables must have the same number of levels!"
msgstr "Semua variabel kategorik harus memiliki jumlah tingkat yang sama!"

msgid "Items must have 2 or more levels!"
msgstr "Item harus memiliki 2 tingkat atau lebih!"

msgid ""
"The variable used for counts must be different from the variable used for "
"categories."
msgstr ""
"Variabel yang digunakan untuk cacah harus berbeda dari variabel yang "
"digunakan untuk kategori."

msgid "Percentage (%%)"
msgstr "Persentase (%%)"

msgid "Levels within variable require at least two or more data points!"
msgstr "Tingkat dalam variabel memerlukan setidaknya dua titik data atau lebih!"

msgid ""
"Please assign a variable to every RM factor (defined in Repeated Measures "
"Factors) within Repeated Measures Cells."
msgstr ""
"Harap tetapkan variabel ke setiap faktor RM (yang didefinisikan dalam Faktor "
"Pengukuran Berulang) dalam Sel Pengukuran Berulang."

msgid "Plots"
msgstr "Plot"

msgid "Available Plot IDs"
msgstr "ID Plot yang Tersedia"

msgid "Plot Grid"
msgstr "Kisi Plot"

msgid "Raincloud Plots"
msgstr "Plot Raincloud"

msgid "Not shown are %s observations due to missing data."
msgstr "Tidak ditampilkan sebanyak %s pengamatan karena data yang hilang."

msgid "Interval around mean is custom."
msgstr "Interval di sekitar rata-rata bersifat kustom."

msgid ""
"<span style = 'color: darkorange'>Error with custom interval: Specified "
"number of clouds does not match clouds in plot.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style = 'color: darkorange'>Kesalahan pada interval kustom: Jumlah "
"awan yang ditentukan tidak sesuai dengan awan dalam plot.</span>"

msgid "Interval around mean represents ± 1 standard error"
msgstr "Interval di sekitar rata-rata mewakili ± 1 kesalahan standar"

msgid "Interval around mean represents ± 1 standard deviation"
msgstr "Interval di sekitar rata-rata mewakili ± 1 standar deviasi"

msgid "Interval around mean represents %d%% confidence interval."
msgstr "Interval di sekitar rata-rata mewakili interval kepercayaan %d%%."

msgid "Points are slightly jittered from their true values."
msgstr "Titik-titik sedikit digeser dari nilai sebenarnya."

msgid ""
"<span style = 'color: darkorange'> Warning! Some data is not "
"shown<br>because it lies outside of the interval set by the custom axis "
"limits.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style = 'color: darkorange'> Peringatan! Beberapa data tidak "
"ditampilkan<br>karena berada di luar interval yang ditetapkan oleh batas "
"sumbu kustom.</span>"

msgid ""
"<span style = 'color: darkorange'> Error with custom orientation: Specified "
"number of clouds does not match clouds in plot.<br>Reverted to default all "
"'R'. Point nudge set to 0.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style = 'color: darkorange'> Kesalahan pada orientasi kustom: Jumlah "
"awan yang ditentukan tidak sesuai dengan awan dalam plot.<br>Dikembalikan ke "
"default semua 'R'. Pergeseran titik diatur ke 0.</span>"

msgid ""
"<span style = 'color: darkorange'> Error with custom color: Specified number "
"of clouds does not match clouds in plot.<br>Ignoring custom color input.</"
"span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style = 'color: darkorange'> Kesalahan pada warna kustom: Jumlah awan "
"yang ditentukan tidak sesuai dengan awan dalam plot.<br>Masukan warna kustom "
"diabaikan.</span>"

msgid "Statistics"
msgstr "Statistik"

msgid "Primary Factor"
msgstr "Faktor Primer"

msgid "Secondary Factor"
msgstr "Faktor Sekunder"

msgid "<i>N</i>"
msgstr "<i>N</i>"

msgid "Lower Whisker"
msgstr "Whisker Bawah"

msgid "25th Percentile"
msgstr "Persentil ke-25"

msgid "75th Percentile"
msgstr "Persentil ke-75"

msgid "Upper Whisker"
msgstr "Whisker Atas"

msgid "%s%% CI for Mean Difference"
msgstr "%s%% CI untuk Selisih Rata-rata"

msgid "Standard Error"
msgstr "Kesalahan Standar"

msgid "Standard Deviation"
msgstr "Standar Deviasi"

msgid "<i>N</i><sub>Total</sub> = %s."
msgstr "<i>N</i><sub>Total</sub> = %s."

msgid "This excludes %s observations due to missing data."
msgstr "Ini tidak termasuk %s pengamatan karena data yang hilang."

msgid "<br>Interval around mean is custom."
msgstr "<br>Interval di sekitar rata-rata bersifat kustom."

msgid "<br>Interval around mean represents %d%% confidence interval."
msgstr "<br>Interval di sekitar rata-rata mewakili interval kepercayaan %d%%."

msgid "%2$s has more than %1$s distinct values and is omitted."
msgid_plural ""
"The following variables have more than %1$s distinct values and are omitted: "
"%2$s."
msgstr[0] ""
"Variabel berikut memiliki lebih dari %1$s nilai berbeda dan dihilangkan: "
"%2$s."

msgid "The decimal point is %s digit to the right of the |"
msgid_plural "The decimal point is %s digits to the right of the |"
msgstr[0] "Titik desimal berada %s digit di sebelah kanan |"

msgid "The decimal point is %s digit to the left of the |"
msgid_plural "The decimal point is %s digits to the left of the |"
msgstr[0] "Titik desimal berada %s digit di sebelah kiri |"
